Meet The Hosts
The Good. The Bad. The Rugby.

Alex Payne

The Good

Former Sky Sports rugby presenter and journalist. The voice of reason keeping Hask and Tins in check most of the time.

James Haskell

The Bad

England and Lions flanker. 77 caps. Unfiltered, unpredictable, and unapologetically entertaining.

Mike Tindall

The Rugby

World Cup winner. 75 England caps. The rugby brain, tactical eye, and the one with the Royal connections.
